[Episode 9]

10
00:02:11,380 --> 00:02:11,900
Press here.

11
00:02:13,620 --> 00:02:14,500
Let me help you up.

12
00:02:14,900 --> 00:02:15,420
Come on.

13
00:02:19,420 --> 00:02:19,850
Take it slow.

14
00:02:22,820 --> 00:02:23,820
Be careful not to hit your head.

15
00:02:28,060 --> 00:02:28,940
This is the antibiotic

16
