00:19:31,480 --> 00:19:31,760
Yes.

349
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:34,660
Were there any doubts
or inconsistencies?

350
00:19:36,280 --> 00:19:37,120
What aspect of doubts

351
00:19:37,500 --> 00:19:38,380
