357
00:19:57,520 --> 00:19:58,700
These two photos

358
00:19:59,280 --> 00:20:01,900
were taken after Ma San-po was detained.

359
00:20:02,580 --> 00:20:03,460
Were you at the scene?

360
00:20:05,340 --> 00:20:05,860
No, I wasn't.

361
00:20:06,600 --> 00:20:07,730
Then why was he injured?

362
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:10,980
According to the statements

363
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:13,660
of Leung Kit and Kwok Wa,

364
00:20:14,100 --> 00:20:14,940
