367
00:20:17,440 --> 00:20:18,180
Those injuries were caused

368
00:20:18,340 --> 00:20:19,620
while we were subduing him.

369
00:20:20,320 --> 00:20:21,010
From what I know,

370
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:23,180
he was aware
of what had happened back then,

371
