378
00:20:39,510 --> 00:20:41,380
in the line of duty

379
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:42,620
while stopping a gunfight

380
00:20:42,640 --> 00:20:43,380
in the old town.

381
00:20:44,120 --> 00:20:45,780
Since then, he's used excessive force

382
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:47,730
