00:20:52,460 --> 00:20:55,050
Ma San-po was electrocuted
while being interrogated.

385
00:20:57,320 --> 00:20:58,330
I'll say it again.

386
00:20:58,800 --> 00:20:59,860
Ma San-po's injuries

387
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:00,780
weren't caused during the interrogation…

388
00:21:00,780 --> 00:21:01,700
No, no, no.

