00:21:02,740 --> 00:21:04,580
Did anyone
in the police station premises

391
00:21:04,580 --> 00:21:05,860
electrocute Ma San-po?

392
00:21:08,740 --> 00:21:09,050
Yes.

393
00:21:09,540 --> 00:21:10,050
Who?

394
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:12,570
Kwok Wa.

395
00:21:15,540 --> 00:21:17,380
But this doesn't make him the mole.

396
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:19,050
Who did he pass info to?

397
00:21:20,300 --> 00:21:21,980
Hon Fui-lung's gang family.

398
00:21:22,540 --> 00:21:23,700
