00:22:34,300 --> 00:22:35,380
Or let me put it another way.

423
00:22:35,800 --> 00:22:37,300
Did you authorize him

424
00:22:37,780 --> 00:22:38,330
to meet Hon Lit?

425
00:22:40,520 --> 00:22:41,460
Even if they had met,

