00:23:08,220 --> 00:23:09,860
It should've been Kwok Wa

440
00:23:10,020 --> 00:23:10,820
and Leung Kit.

441
00:23:11,060 --> 00:23:12,120
From what you remember,

442
00:23:12,160 --> 00:23:13,290
did the reports mention

