00:23:23,300 --> 00:23:24,490
do you mean you don't recall the reports

449
00:23:24,510 --> 00:23:25,780
mentioning the inhaler?

450
00:23:25,780 --> 00:23:26,460
Or

451
00:23:26,460 --> 00:23:28,500
that the reports didn't mention
finding the inhaler at all?

