00:23:32,760 --> 00:23:33,460
and it was submitted

454
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:34,700
for DNA testing.

455
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:36,730
Then why wasn't that mentioned
in the report at the time?

456
00:23:38,680 --> 00:23:39,140
I don't know.

457
00:23:40,220 --> 00:23:41,250
It was a momentary oversight on my part.

458
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:43,180
A momentary oversight

459
00:23:50,600 --> 00:23:52,050
or did someone intentionally hide

