00:25:02,840 --> 00:25:03,860
We suspected Ma San-po

490
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:05,300
was connected to the car crash

491
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:06,560
because the vehicle he was driving

492
00:25:06,700 --> 00:25:08,140
