493
00:25:08,620 --> 00:25:09,760
We allowed him to be released on bail

494
00:25:10,020 --> 00:25:12,140
hoping he would provide some info

495
00:25:12,200 --> 00:25:13,260
to help us solve the case.

496
00:25:13,700 --> 00:25:14,860
These are all our strategies
for solving cases.

497
00:25:14,880 --> 00:25:16,810
Mr. Kwu, you should understand this.

498
00:25:17,700 --> 00:25:17,980
Yes,

499
00:25:18,580 --> 00:25:20,090
